{
  "stem": "444.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and now-- and-- one day, as I said, an SS man or Gestapo man came to the cell and asked me-- could I say it in the Germany language? 'Was machen sie' here, which means, what are you doing over here?",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, well, I just was arrested, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he asked me where I was arrested, and I did not tell him where I was arrested.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told him a lie, that I was arrested on the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So that ended the conversation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And half an hour later, they came to me and took me to interrogation, to the office of the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in that office, the fellow that started the interrogation told me [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He asked me my name and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, [SPEAKING GERMAN] which means, I don't have any records of you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And from that moment on, I started to lie.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I told him that I was brought up as a German, which was no true, because we never spoke German in Poland, even in Germany.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told him that my mother was German, though she had a Polish name, that she was German.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That my father was in the German army, which was true, because during WWI, my father was in the German army, like everybody from the occupied territories.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he interrogated me for two hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to give all kinds of arguments that I was brought up as a German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I told him in the first place, he'd never find a Pole that speaks Polish like I do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I told him muttersprache-- like told him the mother's language, just to tickle a little bit his German nationalism.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
